      "x": 2254,
      "y": 570,
      "width": 902,
      "height": 230,
      "text": "# SKILLS / COMMANDS / MCP — Score & Publish\n\n COMMAND\n   /mkt-repurpose-to-social     (review draft  →  auto-post pipeline)\n\n SKILLS\n   • notion-video-trend-sync    (archive to Notion YouTube Videos DB)\n   • telegram-notifier          (send digest / alerts)\n\n MCP — Blotato  (auto-post hub to YouTube / FB / TikTok / IG / LI / X)\n   blotato_create_post          blotato_create_visual\n   blotato_list_accounts        blotato_get_post_status\n   blotato_create_source        blotato_get_schedule",
